(28, 'test@gmail.com', 'curly Hair', 'normal', 'Frizzy hair', 'Oily', 'redness', '2-3 days', 'Yes,Heavy dandruff', 'None', 'Other Hormonal Issues', 'Disturbed sleep,I wake up atleast once a night', 'High', 'Never', 'yes', 'No', 'Very low in the afternoon', 'dhdia', 'Your curly, frizzy hair needs moisture! Use a moisturizing shampoo and conditioner,  avoid sulfates.  Dandruff requires a medicated shampoo.  Hormonal issues might be impacting your hair; consult a dermatologist.  Prioritize sleep for healthier hair.\n'),
